0 km/s on >~3 kpc scales\nin the Milky Way are in good agreement with observations of external galaxies\nand directly explain why local determinations of the solar motion are\ninconsistent with global measurements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Oct 2014 20:00:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Feb 2015 23:16:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
