ec derived\nin this paper. We find a reasonable agreement between the masses of the\nprogenitors obtained from pre-explosion images and masses derived from\nhydrodynamical models. We estimate the distance to SN 2012ec with the\nStandardized Candle Method (SCM) and compare it with other estimates based on\nother primary and secondary indicators. SNe 2012A, 2012aw and 2012ec all follow\nthe standard relations for the SCM for the use of Type II-P SNe as distance\nindicators.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Oct 2014 15:04:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Jan 2015 14:42:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 26 Jan 2015 16:54:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
